## Slide 12 – PMI Tech Strategic Framework: 4 Excellence Pillars 🏛️

**Layout suggestion:** 4-column pillar layout with icons.

**Key points:**
- **Delivery Excellence** – accelerate time-to-impact (idea → adoption); shorten cycle times, strengthen ownership, ensure measurable business value
- **Service Excellence** – reliable, consistent, secure, resilient services; speed, quality, predictability build trust
- **Organizational Excellence** – strengthen governance, decision-making, platforms & capabilities; align ambition with ability to deliver in an AI-powered world
- **Financial Excellence** – run lean, prioritize clearly, make every dollar count toward scalable value

**Speaker notes:**
